FIG. 11 illustrates an ostial stenosis to which a preferred embodiment of the invention may be applied; and


FIGS. 12a-12i illustrate various embodiments of flexure means (in two dimensions) which may be disposed in the longitudinal struts of preferred embodiments of the present stent.
